OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, England's former deputy chief medical  
OL,6, officer has said his family were       
OL,7, threatened with "having their throats  
OL,8, cut" during the pandemic, as he gave   
OL,9, evidence to the UK Covid inquiry.      
OL,11,FProf Sir Jonathan Van-Tam said that at 
OL,12,Fone point he was asked by police to    
OL,13,Fleave his house over safety concerns.  
OL,15,FHe said receiving hate mail made him   
OL,16,Fconsider stepping down from his role.  
OL,18,FProf Van-Tam warned that officials     
OL,19,Fadvising on future crises may be put   
OL,20,Foff due to the "implications".         
